snippet.title: Project Sparrow - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Early Access Launch Trailer for Project Sparrow, Dids first game on Steam!
Wishlist or purchase on the steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1461600/Project_Sparrow/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/ProjectSparrow_
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/projectspar...
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/Hd8bNd4PTD
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@projectsparrow_
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/dids

All links for Project Sparrow and media assets! https://linktr.ee/ProjectSparrow

Project Sparrow is a competitive arena based archery game for PC. Experience responsive third-person archery combat, and defeat your opponents in 1v1,2v2 or 3v3.

#ProjectSparrow #Steam #EarlyAccess
